Package org.parosproxy.paros.extension

Class ExtensionHookMenu

java.lang.Object
org.parosproxy.paros.extension.ExtensionHookMenu
public class ExtensionHookMenu extends Object
The object to add/hook menus and menu items to the main menu bar and to the main context menu.

The menus added through the hook are removed when the extension is unloaded.

Note: This class is not thread-safe, the menus should be added only through the thread that hooks the extension.

Since:
1.0.0
